@node "Requirements" "System Requirements"
@toc "MAIN"

 @{b}System Requirements@{ub}
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

  An Amiga with AmigaOS 2.1+
  Scalos V39.156+
  MUI 3.3+(?)
  Listtree.mcc, (BetterString.mcc)


 No pref-file or icons exists in this archive. I suggest you download NewIcons
 or a similar package which contains icons.

 The FileTypes-prefs can also import DefIcons-brainfiles (included in the
 NewIcons distribution).

@ENDNODE


@node "Installation" "Installation"
@toc "MAIN"

 @{b}Installation@{ub}
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~

 Put the plugin in Scalos:Plugins/OOP and add it to the plugin-list in ScalosPrefs.
 Then run FileTypes-prefs and customize the filetypes (eg import from a DefIcons-
 brainfile)


@ENDNODE


